passage/?search=John+19%3A31-37&version=NRSV |date=20200419144643 }}; [https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=John+19%3A39-40&version=NRSV 19:39-40] {{Wayback|url=https://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=John+19%3A39-40&version=NRSV |date=20200419135656 }}</ref>

